  "decision_conditions": [
    "<p>The proposed development, as a result of the unjustified removal of historic fabric, would result in an obtrusive and incompatible form of development which causes harm to the heritage asset and would fail to preserve or enhance the character and appearance of the Broadway Market Conservation Area. As such the proposed development is contrary to policies D4 (Delivering Good Design) and HC1 (Heritage Conservation and Growth) of the London Plan 2021, policies LP1 (Design Quality &amp; Local Character) and LP3 (Designated Heritage Assets) of the Hackney Local Plan 2033, the guidance contained within National Planning Policy Framework 2019 and the Hackney Residential Extensions and Alterations SPD 2009.<br></p>"
